snippet: Oakland General Manager Billy Beane is among the most popular general managers with reporters, Baltimore’s Dan Duquette the least. Each brought his team unexpected success in 2012.
abstract: Major League Baseball's general managers meetings begin; Oakland Athletics general manager Billy Beane draws large crowd, while less popular general managers, like Baltimore Orioles GM Dan Duquette, find themselves alone; both Beane and Duquette aim to repeat unexpected success they had in 2012.
lead_paragraph: Oakland General Manager Billy Beane is among the most popular general managers with reporters, Baltimore’s Dan Duquette the least. Each brought his team unexpected success in 2012.

headline.seo: Beane and Duquette, Contrasting Architects of Success
headline.main: Architects of Success, From Shadows or Spotlight
